name: Hello World No.12 (神解)
description:
There are 12 pieces in the "Hello World" series. Each video is composed of images generated by the algorithm, 1500 x 1500 pixel, single channel, color, 12/12 edition.

The program related to the "Hello World" string is usually the most basic demonstration of each programming language, and it is the first program in each programming language. The string is also the first greeting from new AI to humans in the future.
